25|$|TransLink {{replaced}} its Special Provincial Constables, {{who held}} limited <b>policing</b> <b>power,</b> with the Transit Police (legally the South Coast British Columbia Transportation Authority Police Service, or SCBCTAPS) in December 2005. In {{contrast to the}} former TransLink special constables, Transit Police constables have full <b>police</b> <b>powers</b> {{both on and off}} of TransLink property. They are based in New Westminster, BC.|$|R
